{"tid":855264,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"C羅曾與性侵案女主簽署秘密協議 承認女方連續喊不","createTime":"2018-10-10T02:56:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-11T10:11:47.000Z","uid":72652,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"4afca34a7d350a628eb10c330d1f94bdf8af3b8a","tid":855264,"uid":72652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T02:56:54.000Z","msg":"自從《明鏡周刊》曝光C羅09年強奸案細節之後，C羅律師只表態&ldquo;這是侵犯隱私&rdquo;，而並沒有表示&ldquo;這是胡編亂造&rdquo;。當時西班牙媒體就懷疑，C羅強奸案確有其事。如今，《明報周刊》放出了更多細節。C羅在保密協議上的簽名被曝光，C羅也承認女方一直拒絕自己，但自己仍然強行與對方發生了性關系。<br />\n<br />\n這起強奸案發生在2009年夏天，C羅方面在2010年1月12日，與女方馬約爾加方面達成了保密協議。C羅支付37.5萬美元封口費，此外還要承擔馬約爾加進行艾滋病檢查的相關費用。與此同時，馬約爾加必須對此事完全保密。如果馬約爾加接受了記者采訪，那就需要面臨高額的經濟賠償。<br />\n　　在這份協議中，C羅作為當事人一方簽上了自己的名字，他的簽名被《明鏡周刊》曝光。這份簽名意味著，C羅的確與馬約爾加簽署了與強奸有關的保密協議。<br />\n　　在簽署保密協議之前，C羅的律師團隊還對葡萄牙人多次進行了詳細的詢問，他們希望得知每一個細節。這份調查報告，也已經被《明鏡周刊》掌握。在2009年9月對自己律師表態時，C羅明確承認自己違背對方意願進行了性行為。<br />\n　　&ldquo;我從背後進入她，很粗魯。我們沒有改變位置，大概做了5-7分鐘。她說她不想，但她讓我可以這樣做。在整個進程中，都很粗魯。&rdquo;C羅回憶當時發生的事情，&ldquo;她一直說不，一直求我不要那樣做，她說自己與其他女人不一樣。我後來道歉了。她說了不，我中途停了幾次。&rdquo;<br />\n　　但在2009年12月，C羅對自己的律師團隊卻給了另一個版本的說法：&ldquo;我從後面進入她，沒有換體位，時間大概是5-7分鐘。她沒有尖叫，她並沒有打算尋求幫助之類舉動。&rdquo;<br />\n　　美國警方也向《明鏡周刊》確認，馬約爾加在報警時一直在哭，但拒絕給出對方的名字。馬約爾加只是表示自己參加了一個派對，並且在派對中被一名運動員強奸。"},{"pid":"b8930e0dedeb86747317ce1c7524ebe68cdd9836","tid":855264,"uid":72652,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T02:57:36.000Z","msg":"唔好呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n停呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n唔好停呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"387f000ee49fbd265b3d722162e61b7dac3a68f9","tid":855264,"uid":9269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T02:59:48.000Z","msg":"時間大概是5-7分鐘。她沒有尖叫<br />\n又快又細條<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10b7ab25e68103ddb065802e06fed0c2b4362670","tid":855264,"uid":16061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b8930e0dedeb86747317ce1c7524ebe68cdd9836","tid":855264,"uid":72652,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T02:57:36.000Z","msg":"唔好呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n停呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n唔好停呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T02:59:57.000Z","msg":"dont dont dont....dont stop"},{"pid":"643f126b768f4d538caf7d16d2475bab09e41a74","tid":855264,"uid":158613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T03:00:40.000Z","msg":"打J保平安"},{"pid":"4a799bbd5e2611169a20fb267067e5e8dfa2b34d","tid":855264,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T03:02:30.000Z","msg":"隻臭雞要求愛滋病測試？牙朗驚你有愛滋先真"},{"pid":"9d9deeb38f92b4b9c9c551a7ebb3f864bd41b450","tid":855264,"uid":4917,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T03:05:07.000Z","msg":"會拒絕C朗咁不可思義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"810709141f47c65ac046c04f9eb7f84af011fe8a","tid":8552